\updelta_{2X}(x)\xrightleftharpoons[\hat{F}^{-1}]{\hat{F}}\frac{\mathrm{sinc}(kX)}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\qquad\frac{\mathrm{sinc}(Kx)}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\xrightleftharpoons[\hat{F}^{-1}]{\hat{F}}\updelta_{2K}(k)
