将卷积代入 Fourier 变换的定义：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\mathopen{\hat{F}}\left[\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}u(y)\,v(x-y)\dd{y}\right] & =\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\exp(-\ii kx)}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\left[\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}u(y)\,v(x-y)\dd{y}\right]\dd{x}\\
 & =\lim_{h\to\infty}\iint_{\square(x,y;h)}\frac{\exp(-\ii kx)}{\sqrt{2\pi}}u(y)\,v(x-y)\dd{x}\dd{y}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $\square(x,y;h)\coloneqq\left\{ (x,y):\abs{x}<h,\abs{y}<h\right\} $
\end_inset

 是 
\begin_inset Formula $(x,y)$
\end_inset

 平面上的四边形区域。引入坐标变换
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}x\\
y
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}1 & 1\\
1 & 0
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\sigma\\
\tau
\end{bmatrix}\implies\det(\pdv{(x,y)}{(\sigma,\tau)})=1\implies\dd{x}\dd{y}=\dd{\sigma}\dd{\tau}
\]

\end_inset

于是 
\begin_inset Formula $\square(x,y;h)$
\end_inset

 变换为 
\begin_inset Formula $\square(\sigma,\tau;h)\coloneqq\left\{ (\sigma,\tau):\abs{\sigma+\tau}<h,\abs{\sigma}<h\right\} $
